snippet.title: What's In The Basement
snippet.description:
What's in The Basement? Well it's casual, comedic, chaotic, and Canadian! Join your friends Pat, Anton, and Chris as they give unique perspectives on… well… everything. Relationships, Finances, Video Games, The Internet, Pop Culture, and Just Being Alive! No topic is too big, too small, or too weird. We’ll tackle everything that the universe, internet, and you can throw at us.

New Episodes Streamed Every Week!
